get_upper_tri<-function(automobilecontinuous){
  automobilecontinuous[lower.tri(automobilecontinuous)] <- NA
  return(automobilecontinuous)
}

get_upper_tri(automobilecontinuous)

### Group-by fuel.system to see the horsepower, weight and price.

automobilefuel <- automobile %>%
group_by(fuel.system) %>%
summarize(
horsepower = mean(horsepower, na.rm = TRUE),
engine.size = mean(engine.size, na.rm = TRUE),
curb.weight = mean(curb.weight, na.rm = TRUE),
n = n()
)
